OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSmacking children in Wales 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbecomes illegal            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents smacking their children will be
OL,6, illegal in Wales from Monday.          
OL,8,FFirst Minister Mark Drakeford said it  
OL,9,Fwas a "historic" day for children as   
OL,10,FWales becomes the second UK nation to  
OL,11,Fban physical punishment.               
OL,13,FThe legal defence of reasonable        
OL,14,Fpunishment has been removed, so anyone 
OL,15,Fwho smacks a child in their care could 
OL,16,Fbe arrested and prosecuted for assault.
OL,18,FCritics claim the new law was pushed   
OL,19,Fthrough "by those who think they know  
OL,20,Fbetter than parents".                  
